questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you clone any type of website or webpage?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I can clone, copy, and duplicate websites or web pages from various platforms like Figma , Wix, Divi, Joomla, Weebly, Squarespace, Visual Composer, WPBakery, Gutenberg, and any WordPress site.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the website will be seo freindly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, i will do basic seo of entire site and optimize the speed of website

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you do Custom coding ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely Yes! , I can do custom coding , if there is any need of custom code like integrating external libraries or design custom animations or section........

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the design be mobile responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, definitely! I prioritize creating designs that are not only modern and user-friendly but also responsive across different devices, ensuring optimal viewing experiences for your visitors.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I need support or assistance after the project is completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I provide post-delivery support and assistance to ensure your satisfaction. If you encounter any issues or have questions after the project is completed, I'll be available to help you resolve them

reviews.comment: We hired Saad to rebuild our existing website with Webflow. We couldn’t be happier with the outcome. The new website looks identical, all the content has exactly the same URLs they had before, and all the SEO stuff is working. He communicated quite well during the process and he diligently addressed every revision we requested. We will definitely work with him again!

Saad Khan is a truly outstanding website developer! His professionalism, code expertise, and attention to detail made this project a breeze. He demonstrated a deep understanding of the project scope, offering valuable suggestions that elevated the outcome. I expected this level of professionalism since his opening proposal was the only one (of several) that was technically detailed and complete. I am thoroughly impressed and, without hesitation, would work with Saad again. HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!
Saad Khan did an awesome job! His attention to detail and professionalism are top-notch! Working with him was a breeze. Thanks for the excellent cooperation. Highly RECOMMEND! 🙌

I got back a worthless job. This supposed code developer could not even open a photoshop file. I will never use Fiverr again after this. He even charged me an extra $100 to "finish" the job and once again - garbage. Run- don't walk away from this con man.

seller_response.comment:
I encourage potential clients to look beyond this review and consider my track record of positive feedback from clients who appreciate my dedication and professionalism.

I value all feedback but feel compelled to clarify my experience with this buyer...

I completed the project as per our initial agreement and went above and beyond to fulfill her requests. After the initial delivery, she asked for additional work and, after some back-and-forth, agreed to $100 for these revisions. However, upon completion of the additional work, she continued to demand more revisions and raised complaints about aspects that didn’t make sense, despite everything being delivered to a high standard.

What concerns me most is that, after I dedicated significant time and effort to address her requests, she decided to cancel the order and leave this damaging 1-star review. I felt pressured throughout the process, as she even threatened to leave negative feedback unless I completed further work for free. This behavior is not only unprofessional but also undermines the collaborative spirit that I strive for in my client relationships..

Despite my unwavering commitment to customer satisfaction, she chose to cancel the order and left this damaging 1-star review, which misrepresents the quality of my work and the nature of our collaboration.

I’m here to provide quality work and support to those who value open communication and clarity. Thank you for your understanding, and I look forward to working with clients who share these values!
